OL,3,CWho is standing for election in the
OL,4,CMidlands in 2024?
OL,6,FVoters in the Midlands will head to
OL,7,Fthe polls on 2 May to elect local
OL,8,Fcouncillors, Police & Crime
OL,9,FCommissioners and two regional Mayors.
OL,11,FIn parts of the East Midlands voters
OL,12,Fwill elect the first ever East
OL,13,FMidlands Mayor covering Derby,
OL,14,FDerbyshire, Nottingham and
OL,15,FNottinghamshire. Leicester and
OL,16,FLeicestershire are not part of the new
OL,17,FEast Midlands Combined County
OL,18,FAuthority.
