OL,3,CWho is standing for election in the
OL,4,CMidlands in 2024?
OL,6,FConservative leader of Nottinghamshire
OL,7,FCountry Council and Mansfield MP, Ben
OL,8,FBradley has thrown his hat in the
OL,9,Fring. He says he'll spend some of the
OL,10,Fdevolved money on improving roads and
OL,11,Fpublic transport. He's spoken about
OL,12,Fthe importance of being from the area
OL,13,Fand being the right person to
