OL,3,CWho is standing for election in the
OL,4,CMidlands in 2024?
OL,6,FReform UK's candidate is Derby
OL,7,Fcouncillor and Lord Mayor Alan Graves.
OL,8,FHe says people in the East Midlands
OL,9,Fdon't currently have a voice, but he
OL,10,Fwould get rid of the new Combined
OL,11,FCounty Authority, claiming having a
OL,12,FMayor is a waste of money
OL,14,FMatt Relf is an independent candidate
OL,15,Fwho boasts a decade of experience in
OL,16,Fhighways maintenance. He says only an
OL,17,Findependent can stand up to
OL,18,FWestminster and put the East Midlands
OL,19,Ffirst while building the right kind of
OL,20,Fhomes, not just ones that are
OL,21,Fprofitable for developers.
