OL,3,CWho is standing for election in the
OL,4,CMidlands in 2024?
OL,6,FLabour's hopeful is the former MP
OL,7,FClaire Ward. She's worked a lot with
OL,8,Fthe NHS and says she'll be a champion
OL,9,Ffor better services and a voice for
OL,10,Fforgotten communities. She wants to
OL,11,Fincrease the number of affordable
OL,12,Fhomes across the region and help
OL,13,Fcreate thousands of jobs in the green
